{
  "stem": "6803.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And one time in 1944-- It was in--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, they were-- they were-- they were rationing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean in 1943, it started-- started rationing the food.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the Jews were not given all the rations.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We used to get sometimes from neighbors of ours, just sneaking in a little bit of flour, or-- or corn, or beans, or something like that, to be able to survive, you know?",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Bad.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's what I said.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They took all the rights away from the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They had no right to have any stores, own stores.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Took everything away.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we are not allowed to go on trains.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were not allowed to go to school.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Jewish people were not allowed to go to school.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And, uh, we were-- we-- we didn't know what's happening.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We didn't have no radios.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We didn't know what's happening in the world, the news.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And-- and so therefore, I mean, it's uh-- we didn't know what to do.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So all of a sudden, then, we had the news that the Jews were not allowed to go nowhere.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In order for us to be home, that the gendarmes-- or they call it the [HUNGARIAN] in Hungarian-- they came in.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and we would had the food on the stove to cook our lunch, whatever it was.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they came in just like that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They said, we arrest you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Leave everything the way it is, even the food on the stove.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Nothing-- just what you have on your body.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And this is how you have come-- have to come with us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We didn't know what's happening.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't know where we gonna go, what we gonna do.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That time, my father passed away in 1942.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, uh, and I was-- I was alone.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
